Class HashDequeMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap<K,Deque<V>>
java.util.HashMap<K,Deque<V>>
net.mtrop.doom.struct.map.HashDequeMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - the key type.
V - the value type stored.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<K,Deque<V>>
public class HashDequeMap<K,V> extends HashMap<K,Deque<V>>
A hash map that stores deques of a particular type.
Author:
Matthew Tropiano
